Every inhabitant of Kalmykia is a debtor
Residents of the republic increasingly visit the official website of the Office of the Federal Bailiffs Service of Russia in Kazakhstan .
According to the specialists of the department of organizational-control work , informatization and information security of the republican department , in the past eight months more than 140 thousand visits of the site itself were registered , more than 42 thousand - section " Data Bank of executive productions " , 661 payment receipt on payment of debts was downloaded .
According to Valery Bogdanov , Chairman of the Public Council under the UFSSP of Russia in Kazakhstan , almost every inhabitant of the region has debts for utility payments , traffic police fines , bank loans , loans , and no one is insured from unforeseen situations .
But debtors can expect negative consequences , such as a ban on travel abroad .
That is why UFSSP of Russia in Kazakhstan recommends to all who planned a trip abroad , to clarify in the department of bailiffs at the place of residence or on the site www.r08fssprus.ru information on the presence of unpaid debts and to pay them .
The Service has set up a " Data Bank for Execution Proceedings " for the convenience of citizens .
This special electronic application is available not only on the regional sites of the UFSSP of Russia , but also in social networks and mobile communication means iPad , iPhone and smartphone .
The data bank contains information on the execution proceedings initiated by Kalmyk bailiffs against all debtors , - explains the assistant of the head of the Federal Financial Supervision Agency of Russia for Kazakhstan Delgir Bodgaev .
" If there is a debt , the system displays information about the number and date of the enforcement proceedings ; the name of the authority that issued the executive sheet or other act ; its number , amount and type of debt ; the address of the bailiff department ; the name of the bailiff ; the contact phone .
Information on the progress of enforcement proceedings can also be obtained on the portal of public services at : http : / / epgu.gosuslugi.ru "
